         {cards.length === 0 ? (
           <p className="column-empty">No cards</p>
         ) : (
           cards.map(card => (
             <CardTile key={card.id} card={card} onCardClick={onCardClick} />
           ))
         )}
       </div>
+      {footer}
     </section>
   )
 }
```

When `footer` is `undefined` (not passed), React renders nothing — existing column structure is preserved.

